title: [Aurany's Lockpicks]
[Aurany's General Store]
[Aurany's Outfitting]
description: Enclosed by blue watered silk walls, the shop features a serene golden wyvern fountain in the center of its oak floor.  A vaalorian crested pennant hangs under the arched ceiling.  Right near the front is a large cherrywood cabinet and a gold-veined black marble counter.
